THE DECLARATION OF WAR AGAINST

00:02:01.510 --> 00:02:02.646
HUMANITY CAME FROM

00:02:02.646 --> 00:02:05.283
AN UNEXPECTED PERSON.

00:02:05.283 --> 00:02:05.885
&gt;&gt; Nia: ATTENTION,

00:02:05.885 --> 00:02:07.287
HUMANS OF EARTH.

00:02:07.287 --> 00:02:08.824
HEAR ME NOW.

