WE, THE ANTI‐SPIRAL RACES OF

00:02:10.662 --> 00:02:12.666
THE UNIVERSE HAVE DETERMINED

00:02:12.666 --> 00:02:14.335
THAT HUMANS HAVE ACHIEVED

00:02:14.335 --> 00:02:16.272
SPIRAL POWER DANGER LEVEL TWO

00:02:16.272 --> 00:02:17.709
AND ARE A MENACE.

