WHAT’S SHE TALKING ABOUT?

00:02:43.226 --> 00:02:43.928
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: HURRY, PINPOINT THE

00:02:43.928 --> 00:02:44.896
TRANSMISSION ORIGIN!

