IS THAT REALLY NIA SAYING ALL

00:02:56.653 --> 00:02:57.287
THAT CRAZY STUFF?!

00:02:57.287 --> 00:03:01.930
THAT CAN’T BE HER, CAN IT?

00:03:01.930 --> 00:03:03.333
&gt;&gt; Kittan: IT SHUT OFF.

00:03:10.447 --> 00:03:11.617
YEAH, THAT’S WHAT I SAID!

00:03:11.617 --> 00:03:13.353
TRUST YOUR FRIENDLY NEW

00:03:13.353 --> 00:03:13.921
GOVERNMENT COUNCIL!

00:03:13.921 --> 00:03:14.723
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: HUH?! WHAT?!

00:03:14.723 --> 00:03:15.525
