HUH? YOU WANT US TO COMPENSATE

00:03:17.962 --> 00:03:20.535
YOU FOR YOUR HOUSE THAT BURNED?

00:03:20.535 --> 00:03:22.337
YOU DUMB BASTARD!

00:03:22.337 --> 00:03:22.906
DON’T YOU KNOW THAT GURREN

00:03:22.906 --> 00:03:23.874
LAGANN WAS FIGHTING TO PROTECT

00:03:23.874 --> 00:03:24.676
THE CITY?!

00:03:24.676 --> 00:03:25.778
&gt;&gt; Dayakka: WHAT IS GOING ON?

00:03:25.778 --> 00:03:27.247
IT’S CHAOS IN HERE!

00:03:27.247 --> 00:03:27.849
&gt;&gt; Kittan: WHERE YOU BEEN,

00:03:27.849 --> 00:03:28.383
DAYAKKA?!

