&gt;&gt; Guimble: SIR, IT WOULD SEEM

00:03:38.470 --> 00:03:39.740
THE CITIZENS ARE NERVOUS ABOUT

00:03:39.740 --> 00:03:41.242
THAT LITTLE DECLARATION OF WAR.

