&gt;&gt; Jorgun: LISTEN, WE TOUGH!

00:03:58.209 --> 00:03:58.644
WE REAL TOUGH!

00:03:58.644 --> 00:03:59.478
&gt;&gt; Balinbow: QUIT BITCHING AND

00:03:59.478 --> 00:04:00.715
LET US DO JOB!

