&gt;&gt; Dayakka: [sighs]

00:04:04.589 --> 00:04:05.892
WHERE IS ROSSIU NOW?

00:04:05.892 --> 00:04:06.994
&gt;&gt; Guimble: ATTEMPTING TO DEAL

00:04:06.994 --> 00:04:07.896
WITH THE SITUATION.

00:04:07.896 --> 00:04:09.398
PLEASE LEAVE IT TO

00:04:09.398 --> 00:04:10.601
THE CHIEF ADVISOR.

00:04:10.601 --> 00:04:11.770
&gt;&gt; Zorthy: IN OTHER WORDS,

00:04:11.770 --> 00:04:13.473
KEEP US OLD‐TIMERS BUSY WITH

00:04:13.473 --> 00:04:13.974
ALL THESE CALLS.

