&gt;&gt; IT’S A SUCCESS.

00:04:24.596 --> 00:04:25.731
WE’VE ACTIVATED THE

00:04:25.731 --> 00:04:26.800
BIOCOMPUTER.

00:04:26.800 --> 00:04:28.737
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: EXCELLENT. GOOD WORK.

00:04:28.737 --> 00:04:29.706
NOW EVERYBODY LEAVE THE ROOM

00:04:29.706 --> 00:04:30.541
AT ONCE.

