NO ONE IS ALLOWED BACK IN UNTIL

00:04:31.710 --> 00:04:33.279
I GIVE AUTHORIZATION.

00:04:33.279 --> 00:04:38.924
&gt;&gt; VERY GOOD, SIR.

00:04:38.924 --> 00:04:39.659
&gt;&gt; Rossiu: NOW, THEN.

00:04:39.659 --> 00:04:40.728
THIS TIME, YOU’RE GOING TO TELL

00:04:40.728 --> 00:04:42.565
ME EVERYTHING.

00:04:42.565 --> 00:04:43.701
TELL ME ALL THE SECRETS

00:04:43.701 --> 00:04:44.769
OF THIS WORLD.

00:04:44.769 --> 00:04:51.650
WAKE UP, LORDGENOME.

