THIS IS AN EMERGENCY! BACK OFF!

00:06:02.759 --> 00:06:03.727
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: I WON’T!

00:06:03.727 --> 00:06:04.763
&gt;&gt; Simon: THAT’S AN ORDER FROM

00:06:04.763 --> 00:06:05.363
YOUR COMMANDER!

