&gt;&gt; Gimmy: GUNMEN DISPATCHES FALL

00:06:06.967 --> 00:06:08.069
UNDER CHIEF ADVISOR ROSSIU’S

00:06:08.069 --> 00:06:08.771
PURVIEW.

