IF PEOPLE SEE IT FLYING AROUND

00:06:21.462 --> 00:06:22.665
THE CITY, WELL, THEN, IT MIGHT

00:06:22.665 --> 00:06:23.701
CAUSE THEM TO WORRY THAT

00:06:23.701 --> 00:06:24.903
ANOTHER BIG BATTLE IS COMING

00:06:24.903 --> 00:06:25.972
THEIR WAY.

