&gt;&gt; Simon: [laughs]

00:06:29.746 --> 00:06:30.915
YOU SURE CAN MAKE A PERSUASIVE

00:06:30.915 --> 00:06:35.992
CASE THESE DAYS, DARRY.

00:06:35.992 --> 00:06:37.094
YOU WIN.

00:06:37.094 --> 00:06:38.564
TAKE GURREN BACK TO BASE

00:06:38.564 --> 00:06:38.897
WITH YOU.

00:06:38.897 --> 00:06:39.833
I’LL GO OFF IN LAGANN.

00:06:39.833 --> 00:06:41.168
I WON’T DRAW ANY ATTENTION

00:06:41.168 --> 00:06:42.839
IN THIS.

00:06:42.839 --> 00:06:44.475
&gt;&gt; Gimmy: COMMANDER SIMON, WAIT!

00:06:44.475 --> 00:06:45.845
&gt;&gt; Darry: GIMMY, DON’T.

00:06:45.845 --> 00:06:47.014
NO ONE CAN STOP HIM WHEN HE’S

00:06:47.014 --> 00:06:47.916
LIKE THIS.

