&gt;&gt; Leyte: HUH?

00:07:41.790 --> 00:07:43.560
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA’S TRANSMISSION.

00:07:43.560 --> 00:07:47.869
&gt;&gt; Leyte: YEAH. THEY SAW IT.

00:07:47.869 --> 00:07:49.806
&gt;&gt; Simon: DON’T YOU KIDS WORRY!

00:07:49.806 --> 00:07:50.875
’CAUSE NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS,

00:07:50.875 --> 00:07:52.612
WE’LL COME UP WITH SOMETHING

00:07:52.612 --> 00:07:53.881
FOR SURE!

00:07:53.881 --> 00:07:54.883
I DON’T KNOW WHAT THIS HUMANITY

00:07:54.883 --> 00:07:56.853
ANNIHILATION SYSTEM THING IS,

00:07:56.853 --> 00:07:57.989
BUT IT’S NOTHING TO WORRY ABOUT!

00:07:57.989 --> 00:08:03.901
I PROMISE!

00:08:03.901 --> 00:08:04.936
&gt;&gt; Leyte: YOU’RE THE ONE THAT

00:08:04.936 --> 00:08:07.809
WE’RE WORRIED ABOUT, SIMON.

00:08:07.809 --> 00:08:09.011
&gt;&gt; Makken: HE SEEMED PRETTY

00:08:09.011 --> 00:08:10.480
DEPRESSED, DIDN’T HE?

00:08:10.480 --> 00:08:11.550
&gt;&gt; Leyte: SHAME HE’S NOT

00:08:11.550 --> 00:08:12.552
A MECHA.

00:08:12.552 --> 00:08:15.991
THAT, WE COULD FIX.

00:08:32.959 --> 00:08:35.831
&gt;&gt; Simon: NIA, WHERE ARE YOU

00:08:35.831 --> 00:08:37.869
RIGHT NOW?

00:08:37.869 --> 00:08:38.937
WAS THAT REALLY YOU ON THAT

00:08:38.937 --> 00:08:41.743
BROADCAST, NIA?

00:08:56.873 --> 00:08:58.944
NIA!

00:09:06.993 --> 00:09:09.699
